---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="AC Installation in Bastrop, TX | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Professional AC installation in Bastrop, Rosanky, Smithville, Elgin, and Paige. New air conditioning system installation and replacement from your local Bastrop County HVAC experts. Call (512) 924-9744."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>AC Installation</h1>
			<p>Professional air conditioning installation for your home or business</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="service-intro">
				<h2>New AC System Installation in Bastrop County</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					Whether you're replacing an old system or installing AC for the first time, String Prairie Heating & Air provides expert installation services throughout Bastrop County. From newer construction in Tahitian Village and Riverside Grove to older homes in historic downtown Bastrop and Smithville, we help you choose the right system for your needs and budget, then install it with precision and care. We proudly serve Bastrop, Rosanky, Smithville, Elgin, Paige, and all surrounding areas.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-grid">
				<div class="service-main">
					<h3>Signs You Need a New AC System</h3>
					<ul class="service-list">
						<li>
							<strong>Age of System</strong>
							<p>AC systems typically last 10-15 years. Older systems become less efficient and more prone to breakdowns.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Frequent Repairs</strong>
							<p>If you're calling for repairs multiple times per year, replacement may be more cost-effective.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Rising Energy Bills</strong>
							<p>Older systems work harder to cool your home, increasing your energy costs significantly.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Inconsistent Cooling</strong>
							<p>Hot spots or rooms that won't cool properly indicate your system is struggling.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>R-22 Refrigerant</strong>
							<p>Older systems using R-22 (Freon) are expensive to service due to the refrigerant phase-out.</p>
						</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Our Installation Process</h3>
					<div class="process-steps">
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">1</span>
							<h4>Consultation</h4>
							<p>We assess your home, discuss your needs, and recommend the best options for your situation.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">2</span>
							<h4>Load Calculation</h4>
							<p>We perform detailed calculations to ensure your new system is properly sized.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">3</span>
							<h4>Installation</h4>
							<p>Our technicians install your new system following manufacturer specifications and best practices.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">4</span>
							<h4>Testing & Training</h4>
							<p>We test everything thoroughly and show you how to operate your new system.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h3>Benefits of a New AC System</h3>
					<div class="benefits-grid">
						<div class="benefit">
							<h4>Energy Savings</h4>
							<p>Modern systems are significantly more efficient, reducing your monthly energy bills.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="benefit">
							<h4>Better Comfort</h4>
							<p>New systems provide more consistent temperatures and improved humidity control.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="benefit">
							<h4>Quieter Operation</h4>
							<p>Today's AC units run much quieter than older models.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="benefit">
							<h4>Warranty Protection</h4>
							<p>New systems come with manufacturer warranties for peace of mind.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="service-sidebar">
					<div class="cta-box">
						<h3>Ready for a New AC?</h3>
						<p>Contact us for a consultation and learn about your options for a new, efficient cooling system.</p>
						<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">ðŸ”– Book Consultation</a>
						<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
					</div>

					<div class="info-box">
						<h4>Why Choose Us?</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>Family-owned, based in Rosanky</li>
							<li>Proper load calculations for TX climate</li>
							<li>Quality equipment brands</li>
							<li>Professional installation</li>
							<li>Financing options available</li>
							<li>Serving Bastrop County since day one</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="info-box">
						<h4>Service Areas</h4>
						<p>We install AC systems in:</p>
						<ul>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/bastrop">Bastrop & Lost Pines</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/rosanky">Rosanky & String Prairie</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/smithville">Smithville & Buescher</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/elgin">Elgin & McDade</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/paige">Paige & Lincoln</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-banner">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Upgrade Your Comfort Today</h2>
			<p>A new, efficient AC system can save you money and keep your home comfortable for years to come.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">Get Started</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-content {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: white;
	}

	.service-intro {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.service-intro h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.service-main h3 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.service-list li {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--bg-light);
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.service-list li strong {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-list li p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.process-steps {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.step {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.step-number {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		background: var(--primary-blue);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.step h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.step p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.benefits-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.benefit {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red);
	}

	.benefit h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.benefit p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.service-sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta-box {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
	}

	.cta-box h3 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.cta-box p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.btn {
		display: block;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: white;
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: var(--primary-blue);
		color: white;
	}

	.info-box {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.info-box h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.info-box ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.info-box li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-weight: 300;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}

	.info-box li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.info-box a {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.info-box a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.cta-banner {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-banner h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.cta-banner p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.cta-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		background: var(--accent-red);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-radius: 50px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.cta-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.service-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.process-steps,
		.benefits-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>
